Maintainer: dendie sanjaya <dendie_sanjaya@yahoo.com>
Version 1.2.8 stable

#sfLinkCrossAppPlugin

#What: 
    This plugin for resolve link cross application in symfony 1.1 or 1.2 

#How to install:
    first you must dowload package sfLinkCrossAppPlugin, second install plugin from local like this:
 
    {{{
    > php symfony plugin-install file:///your/path/plugin/sfLinkCrossAppPlugin-1.2.8.tgz
    }}}    

    or 

    {{{
     > php symfony plugin-install http://plugins.symfony-project.com/sfLinkCrossAppPlugin
    }}}    

#How to use:
    {{{
     <a href="<?php echo sfLinkCrossApp::linkTo('appName','moduleName/actionName') ?>"> LINK TO APP SAMPLE </a>
    }}} 

    or

    {{{
     <a href="<?php echo sfLinkCrossApp::linkTo('appName') ?>"> DATA INDUK SISWA LINK TO APP SAMPLE </a> 
    }}} 

